### REST Client test file for agent-api Edge Function
### Usage: Install "REST Client" extension in VSCode, set variables below, click "Send Request"

@API_URL = https://zmpitnpmplemfozvtbam.supabase.co/functions/v1/agent-api
@API_KEY = YOUR_API_KEY_HERE

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Health Check (no auth)
### ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{API_URL}}/v1/health

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 2. Health Check — should work without auth
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 3. Unauthorized (no token) — expect 401
### ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{API_URL}}/v1/intervention-types

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 4. Lookup Building by Email
### ──────────────────────────────────────
POST {{API_URL}}/v1/lookup-building-by-email
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joana@example.com"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 5. List Intervention Types
### ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{API_URL}}/v1/intervention-types
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 6. List Assistances for Building
### ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{API_URL}}/v1/buildings/BUILDING_UUID_HERE/assistances?status=open&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 7. Get Assistance Detail
### ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{API_URL}}/v1/assistances/ASSISTANCE_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 8. Create Assistance (with idempotency)
### ──────────────────────────────────────
POST {{API_URL}}/v1/assistances
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: test-idempotency-key-001

{
  "building_id": "BUILDING_UUID_HERE",
  "title": "Elevador parado - teste API",
  "description": "Teste de criação via agent-api",
  "intervention_type_id": "INTERVENTION_TYPE_UUID_HERE",
  "priority": "urgent",
  "source": "email_agent",
  "triggered_by_contact_email": "joana@example.com"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 9. Add Communication
### ──────────────────────────────────────
POST {{API_URL}}/v1/assistances/ASSISTANCE_UUID_HERE/communications
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Teste de comunicação via agente AI",
  "sender_type": "ai_agent"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 10. Save Email Draft
### ──────────────────────────────────────
POST {{API_URL}}/v1/assistances/ASSISTANCE_UUID_HERE/email-log
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: draft-idempotency-key-001

{
  "recipient_email": "joana@example.com",
  "recipient_name": "Joana Silva",
  "subject": "Re: Elevador parado",
  "content": "Exma. Sra. Joana,\n\nA sua reclamação foi registada com o número A-2026-0046.\n\nCom os melhores cumprimentos,\nLuvim Gestão",
  "template_used": "ai_agent_v1",
  "source_email_id": "outlook-msg-id-123",
  "classification": "elevador-parado"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 11. Update Email Log Status (approve draft)
### ──────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{API_URL}}/v1/email-log/EMAIL_LOG_UUID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ai_draft_status": "approved",
  "approved_by": "USER_PROFILE_UUID_HERE"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 12. Import Contacts
### ──────────────────────────────────────
POST {{API_URL}}/v1/import-contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contacts": [
    {
      "email": "joana@example.com",
      "first_name": "Joana",
      "last_name": "Silva",
      "phone": "+351912345678",
      "fraction": "2ESQ",
      "building_code": "146",
      "role": "owner"
    }
  ]
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 13. Test x-api-key header (alternative auth)
### ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{API_URL}}/v1/intervention-types
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}
